    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but trying doesnt change the fact that i'm just constant stress for them. i look at them and i can see how much my mistakes are hurting them. honestly it feels like the only way i could actually help them is to just... stop being a part of their lives. like, if i wasn't around, they could finally have a fresh start without me dragging everything down.",
